Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:58.32,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.74,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:05.08,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.25,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:22.04,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}话不投机 有些后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.99,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}流下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:29.32,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}心随着急切的情感变乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:36.63,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}调整情绪 想知道真实的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:42.38,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}执着于达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:46.06,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}重要的事物在不觉间模糊 溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:51.78,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}今天是崭新的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.21,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.81,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:04.15,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:08.24,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.87,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}一毫米的距离也觉得遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.94,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}匆匆走过的青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.21,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}不会忘 也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.97,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}留下闪耀的一页
